    "The various categories of cybersecurity solutions in this function are detailed below;• Asset management Asset management encompasses the identification and monitoring of the various elements, such as information, personnel, equipment, systems, and facilities, that contribute to an organization's objectives and are proportionate to their importance and risk strategies.",
    "This includes activities like discovering, cataloging, overseeing, and tracing assets to ensure their protection.",
    "With the emergence of diverse platforms, ranging from operational technology systems and Internet of Things (IoT) devices to on-premises and cloud-based services, cybersecurity asset management has become increasingly intricate.",
    "This proliferation of asset types, coupled with the growing trend of remote work, has led to a distributed asset landscape that poses challenges in terms of management and inventory.",
    "However, the implementation of an AI-powered asset management system can alleviate many of these difficulties by providing advanced intelligence to support human teams in addressing these key use cases.• Asset inventory management-Asset discovery and management are vital for complete visibility and control over assets in an extended network."
  ],
